WEBVTT

01:59.120 --> 02:00.040
Bai Ze.

02:00.720 --> 02:01.680
What was that?

02:05.560 --> 02:08.400
-Ji Can, a Lonescale.
-Ji Can?

02:09.400 --> 02:10.440
Unlike your name,

02:11.039 --> 02:14.080
"Ji" here refers to loneliness.

02:16.000 --> 02:17.920
Do you feel lonely right now?

02:21.120 --> 02:22.360
Not just now.

02:24.320 --> 02:25.760
It's always been this way.

02:27.200 --> 02:29.760
Chi Wen's dragon scale,
which you once swallowed,

02:29.840 --> 02:31.240
<i>has been inside you,</i>

02:32.800 --> 02:36.080
feeding on your loneliness all this time.

02:36.160 --> 02:39.440
Finally, it took form, becoming a demon.

02:40.480 --> 02:42.080
A demon named Lonescale.

02:43.640 --> 02:47.720
Over the years, you held high positions
as the Dragon Deity,

02:48.240 --> 02:49.600
<i>beloved by everyone.</i>

02:50.120 --> 02:52.960
But no one really understands
your loneliness.

02:57.760 --> 02:59.720
<i>You stay alone in the Scale Cave,</i>

03:00.600 --> 03:04.040
<i>accompanied only by your shadow.</i>

03:05.760 --> 03:07.240
<i>Over the years,</i>

03:08.320 --> 03:10.600
your loneliness gave birth to this demon.

03:11.680 --> 03:15.360
It embodies the untold loneliness
deep in your heart.

03:18.160 --> 03:19.400
Throughout the ages,

03:21.120 --> 03:23.320
there have been only two Lonescales.

03:24.120 --> 03:28.440
Because only the loneliest beings
can give birth to this demon.

03:30.880 --> 03:32.080
Two?

03:34.600 --> 03:36.280
Where's the other one?

03:47.560 --> 03:48.680
Do you remember?

03:49.480 --> 03:53.840
Lu Wuyi keeps saying
that you carry a unique fragrance.

03:53.920 --> 03:55.240
<i>Master Dragon Deity.</i>

03:57.000 --> 03:59.160
You have such a special fragrance.

04:00.480 --> 04:02.760
I've never smelled it in the mortal world.

04:02.840 --> 04:08.120
How come you've obtained a fragrance?

04:09.600 --> 04:11.120
Is it because of him?

04:11.200 --> 04:15.360
Dragon bone, dragon saliva,
dragon blood, and dragon scale

04:15.440 --> 04:16.519
all carry a fragrance.

04:17.200 --> 04:20.640
Lonescale is essentially a dragon scale
feeding on your loneliness.

04:21.160 --> 04:24.720
Therefore, it also carries a unique scent.

04:24.800 --> 04:29.640
But this scent makes people sad,

04:31.080 --> 04:34.320
as if they're hollowed out.

04:35.120 --> 04:36.920
But this fragrance

04:38.360 --> 04:40.240
leaves a hollow ache in the heart,

04:40.320 --> 04:44.960
like a valley full of blooming flowers,
yet utterly devoid of people.

04:45.040 --> 04:49.160
It's like flowers in an empty valley
or thick snow on an ancient temple.

04:49.240 --> 04:52.560
The lonelier you are inside,
the stronger this scent becomes.

04:53.400 --> 04:57.640
Master Dragon Deity,
your fragrance seems to be lighter.

04:57.720 --> 05:00.240
Why is your fragrance fading?

05:00.320 --> 05:01.760
Nonsense.

05:06.200 --> 05:08.800
Then why can't anyone smell it,

05:09.880 --> 05:11.240
including me?

05:11.320 --> 05:14.240
Only those who truly understand
your loneliness

05:15.600 --> 05:17.040
can smell it.

05:20.640 --> 05:23.160
It's true. I'm not lying to you.

05:26.680 --> 05:29.360
As we approach the end,
things get more unpredictable,

05:29.440 --> 05:32.840
and you grow more hesitant and hurt.

05:33.720 --> 05:34.840
Right?

05:38.000 --> 05:39.280
I'm not hesitant.

05:40.880 --> 05:42.160
I'm afraid.

05:43.960 --> 05:47.640
I'm scared that after
so many years of struggle,

05:49.080 --> 05:51.800
I'd fail to live up to your expectations

05:53.680 --> 05:55.240
and let you down

05:56.840 --> 05:58.120
in the end.

05:59.240 --> 06:00.920
But you're also scared to succeed.

06:02.080 --> 06:03.120
Aren't you?

06:03.880 --> 06:05.480
Because to reach the end,

06:05.560 --> 06:08.400
you must accept
the fact that you'd lose her.

06:11.080 --> 06:14.840
That's why I cherish
every moment I have with her.

06:15.360 --> 06:17.440
Why are you torturing yourself?

06:17.520 --> 06:19.320
I don't want to lose her.

06:21.400 --> 06:22.880
But it's inevitable.

06:27.000 --> 06:28.320
I have no choice.

06:30.160 --> 06:32.240
But you have to make a choice.

06:33.720 --> 06:36.000
Or you'll be devoured by Lonescale.

06:37.400 --> 06:38.920
What will happen

06:42.560 --> 06:44.000
if I am devoured?

06:47.680 --> 06:48.880
Master Dragon Deity.

06:58.160 --> 07:00.440
Master Bai Ze. What brought you here?

07:03.200 --> 07:04.280
How's everything going?

07:05.120 --> 07:08.640
The Spirit-Binding Ring
and the Dragon Deity's Power of Han Ba

07:08.720 --> 07:10.160
were snatched away by Lu Wuyi.

07:13.160 --> 07:15.240
What exactly does she want?

07:15.320 --> 07:16.880
No idea.

07:17.600 --> 07:19.160
She simply vanished.

07:20.440 --> 07:22.400
The Dragon Deity's Power is crucial.

07:22.480 --> 07:24.040
We must find her.

07:28.120 --> 07:33.240
Master, why did your fragrance
suddenly grow so intense?

07:35.720 --> 07:37.360
You also smell it, Commander Li?

07:38.880 --> 07:41.240
I don't think you could smell it before.

07:42.040 --> 07:42.880
That's right.

07:43.440 --> 07:45.760
Lu Wuyi kept mentioning it,

07:47.560 --> 07:48.760
and I've been curious.

07:49.360 --> 07:54.600
I didn't expect this fragrance
to be so heartbreaking.

07:56.160 --> 07:57.400
It feels like

07:59.200 --> 08:03.400
entering an ancient temple
abandoned in the heavy snow.

08:18.920 --> 08:23.280
ARTISAN BAMBOO CRAFTS, EASTFIELD RICE SHOP

08:23.360 --> 08:27.920
ARTISAN BAMBOO CRAFTS

08:49.640 --> 08:50.600
I know him.

08:51.200 --> 08:54.280
I've seen him at the Dragon Deity Temple.
He's Master Chi Wen.

08:54.360 --> 08:56.200
The Dragon Deity really descended.

08:56.280 --> 08:58.080
We're saved.

08:58.720 --> 08:59.560
Yes!

08:59.640 --> 09:02.280
-Master Chi Wen.
-Help us.

09:03.000 --> 09:05.640
-Master Chi Wen.
-Please help us!

09:07.040 --> 09:08.360
Master Chi Wen.

09:09.800 --> 09:11.200
Master Chi Wen.

09:18.080 --> 09:20.080
I know him. He's Master Chi Wen.

09:20.160 --> 09:21.680
I've seen him at the Dragon Deity Temple.

09:21.760 --> 09:23.160
Master Chi Wen. Master Chi Wen.

09:23.240 --> 09:25.080
Master Chi Wen.
Please bestow rainfall upon us.

09:25.160 --> 09:26.720
Please help us.

09:26.800 --> 09:27.800
Master Chi Wen.

09:27.880 --> 09:29.200
Please help us.

09:29.280 --> 09:31.520
Please help us.

09:31.600 --> 09:32.840
He is not a Dragon Deity.

09:32.920 --> 09:34.080
He can't help us at all.

09:34.160 --> 09:36.920
We've been worshipping and admiring him,
but he doesn't do anything.

09:37.000 --> 09:38.280
-Get him.
-Get him.

10:08.320 --> 10:09.160
Where's Master Dragon Deity?

10:09.240 --> 10:10.600
-Where is he?
-Where did he go?

10:10.680 --> 10:12.120
-He's gone.
-Master is gone.

10:12.760 --> 10:13.800
Where did he go?

10:13.880 --> 10:15.000
Where's Master Dragon Deity?

10:28.440 --> 10:30.200
<i>What Ji Ling said is true.</i>

10:30.280 --> 10:32.120
<i>Lu Wuyi deceived us.</i>

10:33.040 --> 10:35.600
<i>You weren't the one who cast</i>
<i>the Word Magic on Mu Long.</i>

10:36.200 --> 10:37.400
<i>It was my sister.</i>

10:38.360 --> 10:40.600
<i>Ji Ling. I'm sorry.</i>

10:43.120 --> 10:44.720
<i>My name is Mu Long.</i>

10:44.800 --> 10:48.920
<i>My mother named me Mu Long,</i>
<i>which means "admiring dragons".</i>

10:50.120 --> 10:54.760
<i>Our entire family sees</i>
<i>Master Dragon Deity as an almighty.</i>

10:54.840 --> 10:56.920
<i>They all believed in him.</i>

10:57.000 --> 10:58.800
<i>But I never did.</i>

10:59.400 --> 11:00.800
<i>Because I thought</i>

11:01.320 --> 11:06.280
<i>if there were dragons in this world</i>
<i>that could eliminate disaster,</i>

11:06.360 --> 11:08.760
<i>then no creature would be suffering.</i>

11:09.320 --> 11:12.240
<i>So I didn't believe in him.</i>
<i>Nor did I worship him.</i>

11:12.760 --> 11:15.200
<i>Therefore, I hated my name.</i>

11:15.960 --> 11:21.120
Is Master Dragon Deity aware
of all the worldly suffering?

11:39.520 --> 11:44.040
<i>But then, my great-grandmother</i>
<i>fell ill after a stroke.</i>

11:44.120 --> 11:46.040
<i>I had no choice.</i>

11:46.120 --> 11:49.880
<i>I… I… I had to worship and beg him.</i>

11:49.960 --> 11:53.240
At that moment, I finally realized
what he tried to show us.

11:53.840 --> 11:57.280
What sustains us through suffering
and helps us defeat evil…

11:57.360 --> 11:59.320
…is not the blessing of the deities

11:59.960 --> 12:02.000
but the hope we have.

12:03.560 --> 12:04.760
Here you are.

12:08.480 --> 12:10.200
Lu Wuyi will come.

12:12.080 --> 12:13.680
I have to stop her.

12:14.280 --> 12:15.560
Lu Wuyi will come?

12:16.160 --> 12:17.080
Yes.

12:18.480 --> 12:19.560
I dreamed of it.

12:21.880 --> 12:22.880
And

12:24.680 --> 12:25.840
I was here too.

12:25.920 --> 12:27.560
No.

12:27.640 --> 12:29.000
No.

12:29.520 --> 12:30.680
Ji Ling.

12:30.760 --> 12:31.760
Dream?

12:32.400 --> 12:35.400
Like Ji Ling,
I've also had a similar dream.

12:37.920 --> 12:41.520
In that dream,
you were possessed by Jiu Ying

12:42.360 --> 12:44.040
after gathering
all the Dragon Deity's Power.

12:44.120 --> 12:47.080
Jiu Ying manipulated you to kill Chi Wen.

12:47.160 --> 12:49.520
So Ji Ling is not trustworthy.

12:52.160 --> 12:54.720
But I've also seen him
in Chi Wen's memory.

12:55.400 --> 12:58.480
<i>His eyes were crystal clear,</i>
<i>free from all impurity.</i>

12:59.120 --> 13:03.040
I'm reluctant to believe
that he covets the dragon throne.

13:04.320 --> 13:08.400
Otherwise, there wouldn't be
so many outstanding double-flower hunters

13:08.480 --> 13:10.160
<i>who vow to follow him.</i>

13:10.920 --> 13:14.680
This moment has been repeated
countless times.

13:15.680 --> 13:19.280
<i>All of us have been going back</i>
<i>in time over and over.</i>

13:20.920 --> 13:24.240
<i>Those are not dreams,</i>
<i>but what really happened.</i>

13:26.120 --> 13:28.320
It was repeated too many times

13:30.280 --> 13:32.600
and was etched in the depths
of our consciousness

13:34.600 --> 13:36.040
like a vague dream.

13:43.520 --> 13:44.840
Now,

13:47.280 --> 13:48.440
I have finally realized

13:50.200 --> 13:52.160
<i>what exactly Wu wanted to do.</i>

13:55.560 --> 13:57.280
The man she's trying to save

14:00.800 --> 14:01.920
is not Wu Wangyan.

14:04.720 --> 14:08.960
The years are too long, long enough
to change our original intention.

14:11.320 --> 14:12.840
People change.

14:21.400 --> 14:23.040
Ji Ling can lie to me.

14:24.800 --> 14:27.760
But Lu Wuyi can also lie to you.

14:29.840 --> 14:34.680
One of them has to be lying.

14:38.320 --> 14:39.800
Wu lied to me.

14:41.520 --> 14:42.960
I lied to her too.

14:44.840 --> 14:48.400
We are both lying.

14:53.280 --> 14:54.600
Ji.

14:55.440 --> 14:56.680
You lied to me.

14:59.840 --> 15:01.840
You've been lying to me.

15:35.480 --> 15:37.000
So what are you going to do?

15:45.160 --> 15:46.520
No matter what,

15:49.400 --> 15:51.600
I must retrieve the Dragon Deity's Power.

15:56.560 --> 16:00.480
SERVE THE SCALES, UPHOLD THE RIGHT

16:03.040 --> 16:03.920
Stop.

16:09.440 --> 16:10.280
Wu.

16:13.360 --> 16:15.600
Why can she activate
the Spirit-Binding Ring?

16:19.840 --> 16:21.400
She has the dragon's scent.

16:24.400 --> 16:25.560
How come?

16:29.440 --> 16:30.360
It's the Lonescale.

16:30.440 --> 16:32.760
She has the sacred power of a Lonescale.

16:33.840 --> 16:35.720
The Lonescale is transformed
from dragon scales.

16:35.800 --> 16:38.280
The Spirit-Binding Ring
was confused by the scent

16:38.360 --> 16:39.840
and recognized her as its master.

16:40.480 --> 16:45.000
But why does she carry
the scent of a Lonescale?

16:59.040 --> 17:00.240
Wu.

17:02.520 --> 17:04.079
We are still

17:05.800 --> 17:07.800
in a rewind.

17:09.160 --> 17:10.280
Right?

17:20.920 --> 17:23.119
You've been through

17:26.440 --> 17:28.079
countless rewinds,

17:30.360 --> 17:32.160
enduring all the pain

17:34.200 --> 17:36.360
just to save someone.

18:03.760 --> 18:05.360
The person you've wanted to save

18:10.040 --> 18:11.520
has always been me.

18:15.520 --> 18:16.440
Right?

18:23.840 --> 18:25.040
Deception.

18:27.720 --> 18:29.840
Perhaps only lies and deception

18:32.680 --> 18:34.560
can help me save you.

18:36.200 --> 18:38.480
Ji Ling. Ji Ling.

18:44.720 --> 18:45.840
Ji Ling.

20:06.600 --> 20:07.480
Yes.

20:17.040 --> 20:20.960
FIRST TIME

20:21.040 --> 20:24.040
I have sent Wu Wangyan's body
back to the Formless Moon.

20:24.120 --> 20:27.040
He will be resurrected
from the Primordial Sacred Spring soon.

20:27.760 --> 20:30.800
And Wu Shiguang
is about to slay the dragon.

20:32.000 --> 20:34.160
I have played this game
with you for years.

20:36.200 --> 20:38.000
The game is finally settled.

20:38.840 --> 20:41.040
I've accompanied you
on this final journey.

20:42.640 --> 20:44.520
Once this heavy rain falls,

20:46.160 --> 20:50.200
my mission will be completed.

20:57.600 --> 20:59.960
No one can control
three demon powers simultaneously.

21:01.320 --> 21:02.880
Your spiritual veins will be torn

21:05.760 --> 21:06.920
and your soul shattered.

21:07.000 --> 21:08.640
I've made up my mind.

21:10.880 --> 21:12.200
Just let me do it.

21:22.320 --> 21:25.840
By the fox's call, wrathful sandstorm.

21:47.560 --> 21:51.400
Eastern Purple Lightning,
grant me your power.

21:58.280 --> 22:00.520
Ji Ling. Ji Ling.

23:12.040 --> 23:13.080
Ji Ling.

23:17.480 --> 23:18.480
Ji Ling.

23:19.440 --> 23:20.600
Is that you?

23:22.760 --> 23:24.120
I'm not Ji Ling.

23:24.880 --> 23:26.840
I'm the demon in him.

23:28.480 --> 23:29.680
A Lonescale.

23:32.760 --> 23:34.560
You should be very familiar

23:36.280 --> 23:37.600
with my scent.

23:41.720 --> 23:43.040
The fragrance.

23:44.400 --> 23:45.520
So it's you.

23:48.360 --> 23:50.360
Are you upset?

23:53.480 --> 23:54.400
Yes.

23:55.640 --> 23:57.520
Do you regret it?

23:57.600 --> 24:00.400
Do you want to start over?

24:01.320 --> 24:02.280
Yes.

24:04.360 --> 24:09.320
I have the ability to rewind time.

24:10.040 --> 24:14.320
I can take you back in time
to change everything.

24:18.360 --> 24:19.880
Go back in time?

24:22.240 --> 24:24.200
Why do you have this power?

24:25.280 --> 24:26.720
Ji Ling

24:28.600 --> 24:30.280
lived his entire life in remorse.

24:31.000 --> 24:33.480
<i>He had always wanted to go back in time</i>

24:34.280 --> 24:35.840
<i>to change everything.</i>

24:37.680 --> 24:42.680
If I hadn't run out of sacred power,

24:44.720 --> 24:47.520
<i>I could have saved Yuan Wuhuo's brother.</i>

24:50.080 --> 24:51.760
<i>If I can go back in time</i>

24:53.960 --> 24:55.440
<i>and choose again,</i>

24:59.680 --> 25:01.960
will I still swallow that dragon scale?

25:10.000 --> 25:11.800
Is it snowing in South Mountain now?

25:15.080 --> 25:16.280
In the next life,

25:18.080 --> 25:21.360
be a carefree blind fox.

25:23.720 --> 25:24.880
It's summer.

25:27.240 --> 25:29.240
There must be plenty of raspberries

25:32.440 --> 25:33.920
by the Yumian Lake now.

25:37.480 --> 25:41.320
All his remorse turned into an obsession

25:43.080 --> 25:45.360
and was absorbed by the dragon scale.

25:45.440 --> 25:47.360
That's how I came into being.

25:48.320 --> 25:53.200
His hundred years of obsession
gave me the ability to go back in time.

25:54.720 --> 25:56.560
Do you wish to go back in time

25:57.840 --> 26:00.040
to save your beloved one?

26:00.120 --> 26:01.680
Yes, I do.

26:07.720 --> 26:10.040
But I have Jiu Ying fragments in me.

26:12.400 --> 26:13.760
He'll notice it.

26:14.840 --> 26:17.120
The world of rewinds I create

26:18.640 --> 26:22.640
is a closed universe free
from the laws of the outside world.

26:24.280 --> 26:25.960
Jiu Ying can't monitor you.

26:26.560 --> 26:31.240
You can do whatever you want
without any fear of failure.

26:32.080 --> 26:34.320
You can do it over and over again,

26:35.960 --> 26:36.800
as long as…

26:39.440 --> 26:40.800
As long as what?

26:41.680 --> 26:44.840
As long as your physical form
can withstand it.

26:45.720 --> 26:49.440
Each rewind rewrites the past

26:50.240 --> 26:52.760
and inflicts serious damage on you.

26:52.840 --> 26:53.960
I'm not afraid.

26:58.200 --> 26:59.800
Even if I have to perish,

27:00.840 --> 27:02.480
I'm not afraid.

27:28.480 --> 27:29.440
Go ahead.

27:30.480 --> 27:33.200
I can send you back
to the midnight three days ago.

27:35.240 --> 27:36.320
Wait for me.

27:39.200 --> 27:40.600
Wait for me.

27:48.480 --> 27:49.680
Why are you helping me?

27:51.120 --> 27:52.880
Because I also want to save Ji Ling.

27:54.800 --> 27:56.240
He is a kind person,

27:58.800 --> 27:59.800
yet pitiful.

28:02.480 --> 28:03.760
He is not pitiful.

28:07.880 --> 28:08.960
He is a kind

28:10.560 --> 28:11.760
and great man.

28:54.640 --> 29:00.560
FIRST REWIND

29:48.040 --> 29:50.000
I tried over and over again…

29:52.280 --> 29:53.600
and kept failing.

29:54.760 --> 29:56.120
I wouldn't give up.

31:03.520 --> 31:04.600
Wait for me.

31:31.280 --> 31:32.560
Wait for me.

32:23.200 --> 32:24.320
Wait for me.

32:30.560 --> 32:31.560
Wait for me.

33:20.280 --> 33:21.320
Ji Ling.

33:32.040 --> 33:33.160
Wu.

33:33.960 --> 33:34.840
Ji Ling.

33:43.560 --> 33:44.640
Ji Ling.

33:45.160 --> 33:46.360
I know.

33:47.480 --> 33:50.920
I know you did all this to kill Jiu Ying.

33:51.600 --> 33:54.360
You didn't want me to know
and kept it from me.

33:55.320 --> 33:57.880
Why are you so cruel to yourself?

34:02.880 --> 34:03.800
Wu.

34:06.280 --> 34:07.480
For me,

34:09.400 --> 34:10.840
this is already

34:13.800 --> 34:15.520
the best result.

34:18.760 --> 34:21.800
At least, I was
the true Dragon Deity for once.

34:24.440 --> 34:28.480
It's just that I don't know

34:29.639 --> 34:32.320
whether they will remember me

34:34.719 --> 34:36.760
and this pouring rain.

34:39.639 --> 34:44.600
The little fox who pretended
to be a dragon for a hundred years

34:45.280 --> 34:47.760
lived up to the name of the Dragon Deity.

34:50.159 --> 34:51.920
You're still lying to me.

34:52.960 --> 34:54.400
Because you know

34:56.040 --> 34:59.800
that if Jiu Ying dies, I'll die too.

35:01.400 --> 35:03.240
I know I can't save you.

35:05.720 --> 35:07.800
So I'll die with you.

35:09.000 --> 35:10.240
No.

35:11.480 --> 35:12.480
Wu.

35:14.040 --> 35:15.200
Don't cry.

35:17.520 --> 35:18.640
Don't cry.

35:20.000 --> 35:21.920
-I'll wait for you over there.
-No.

35:22.720 --> 35:25.720
I'll pick you up
with a bundle of flowers in hand.

35:26.640 --> 35:28.920
A huge bundle.

35:30.680 --> 35:31.800
This way,

35:33.320 --> 35:35.080
you won't be afraid.

35:36.560 --> 35:38.000
And I won't be afraid.

35:43.320 --> 35:45.360
If… If…

35:46.760 --> 35:49.520
If we can, I…

35:51.280 --> 35:52.320
I want to…

36:02.280 --> 36:04.560
No.

36:04.640 --> 36:05.720
No.

36:17.120 --> 36:19.920
No. No.

36:21.120 --> 36:22.640
Ji Ling.

36:22.720 --> 36:25.840
No. Ji Ling.

36:26.720 --> 36:29.320
No.

36:30.720 --> 36:32.760
No.

36:35.360 --> 36:38.600
No.

36:46.360 --> 36:47.680
No.

37:17.320 --> 37:18.320
Wait for me.

37:21.520 --> 37:22.520
Wait for me.

37:26.640 --> 37:28.440
I've tried a million ways

37:31.960 --> 37:34.360
and experienced unimaginable hardships.

37:36.400 --> 37:37.560
In the end,

37:38.880 --> 37:40.440
I realized…

37:40.520 --> 37:42.280
If you take Ji Ling's ring,

37:42.880 --> 37:47.240
he can't activate his demon power
and won't be able to sacrifice himself.

37:48.640 --> 37:49.520
No.

37:52.040 --> 37:53.840
I've tried it.

38:06.480 --> 38:07.640
Why?

38:07.720 --> 38:09.880
TWENTY-SIXTH REWIND

38:09.960 --> 38:11.680
Why doesn't it work?

38:14.000 --> 38:17.680
<i>Taking the ring alone</i>
<i>doesn't change Ji Ling's fate.</i>

38:18.960 --> 38:23.280
I must relieve this drought
with the Dragon Deity's Power.

38:24.760 --> 38:27.120
No. No.

38:29.280 --> 38:30.560
Why not?

38:31.160 --> 38:35.080
Once the drought is relieved,
The Dragon Deity's Power will dissipate.

38:35.160 --> 38:36.840
It will dissipate?

38:38.000 --> 38:40.880
The Dragon Deity's Power
breaks through all the barriers

38:40.960 --> 38:42.160
and removes all spells.

38:42.240 --> 38:44.400
Didn't Xiaowei lift the Fox-Allure Spell

38:44.480 --> 38:46.960
for the people of Luo'an
with the Dragon Deity's Power?

38:48.760 --> 38:52.280
Lu Wuyi doesn't just want
to relieve the drought.

38:53.080 --> 38:54.800
She also wants to save Ji Ling.

38:56.600 --> 39:00.320
The drought in Luo'an is destined
to be resolved with Ji Ling's sacrifice.

39:01.440 --> 39:03.720
No matter how many rewinds she attempts,

39:03.800 --> 39:06.160
she can't change the long-written ending.

39:06.960 --> 39:10.200
If she forcibly relieves the drought
with the Dragon Deity's Power,

39:10.920 --> 39:12.840
she'd be intervening
with Ji Ling's destiny

39:12.920 --> 39:14.120
against the will of heaven.

39:15.280 --> 39:19.000
The Dragon Deity's Power
will naturally dissipate.

39:20.160 --> 39:22.680
Then our long-standing plan…

39:23.480 --> 39:24.320
Wu.

39:26.000 --> 39:27.880
-No.
-Don't.

39:27.960 --> 39:29.920
Wuyi. Don't.

39:30.920 --> 39:31.840
Don't.

39:35.880 --> 39:37.000
I insist.

39:39.600 --> 39:42.920
Xiaowei. Ms. Yu is too badly injured.
She's beyond saving.

39:43.520 --> 39:44.760
You will defy the will of heaven

39:44.840 --> 39:46.680
if you save her
with the Dragon Deity's Power.

39:46.760 --> 39:48.920
You will be reduced to nothing.

39:49.000 --> 39:50.120
<i>I insist.</i>

39:52.360 --> 39:53.720
Even if you resent me,

39:55.000 --> 39:57.120
and even if I'm reduced to nothing,

39:58.200 --> 39:59.680
I want you alive.

40:02.920 --> 40:04.280
I won't let you die.

40:24.560 --> 40:28.320
I have seen through your moves
in my countless rewinds.

40:28.960 --> 40:30.600
Your spells can't contain me.

40:31.280 --> 40:33.520
My sacred power has surpassed yours.

40:34.320 --> 40:36.080
You can't stop me.

40:51.280 --> 40:52.280
I have no sacred power.

40:54.240 --> 40:56.000
You have my ring.

40:59.600 --> 41:01.520
But I must stop you.

41:04.920 --> 41:05.840
Wuyi.

41:08.680 --> 41:10.360
Don't do this for me.

41:12.400 --> 41:13.520
It's not worth it.

41:15.600 --> 41:16.680
Ji Ling.

41:18.520 --> 41:19.880
Let go.

41:39.160 --> 41:40.360
Wuyi.

41:40.440 --> 41:41.440
Dreamfall.

42:04.120 --> 42:07.760
Thank you for getting rid of them for me.

42:16.920 --> 42:19.200
Hand over the Dragon Deity's
Power of Han Ba,

42:19.280 --> 42:20.800
and I will spare you.

42:22.800 --> 42:24.240
Yuan Wuhuo.

42:42.200 --> 42:43.640
You've been hiding for ages.

42:45.120 --> 42:46.960
Finally, you can't help but show up.

42:48.320 --> 42:52.080
Since you knew it was me,
why didn't you point it out?

42:53.640 --> 42:54.840
You know

42:56.320 --> 42:58.880
what people become after they go through

43:00.120 --> 43:01.720
dozens of rewinds?

43:04.120 --> 43:04.960
What?

43:06.760 --> 43:08.120
They become deities.

43:17.400 --> 43:20.560
They know everything.

43:27.120 --> 43:32.240
To the deities, both you and Li Jie

43:34.240 --> 43:35.680
are insignificant.

43:37.680 --> 43:39.120
Why should I care?

43:42.160 --> 43:45.280
Triple-flower paints the day.
All things live and perish.

43:45.360 --> 43:48.000
Before me, all becomes clear. Appear.

43:59.040 --> 44:00.320
A triple-flower mark?
